Synthesis I: Basics

Gather the 3 ingredients!

Combat I: Basics

Lorr

Win the consecutive battle against the monster mob!

Predictology

Respond accurately and catch your fish!

Pharmacy I

Give water to the farm!

Minerology

Find minerals and dig!
  • To get an [A]
  • you must mine the northern-most point (which yields [Legien Steel])
  • plus at least one of the two southern locations.

Combat II: Burst

Lorr

Activate a Burst and defeat the target!

「Stone Watcher」 is weak to all three elements. You must Burst and defeat the boss in under 30 minutes (cards) to get an [A].

Naturology I: Basics

Zeppel

Gather fruits from the Millennium tree!

Gather [Night-in-Grape] and/or [Sunrise Orange] to get an [A].

Synthesis III: Derivation

Isolde

Synthesize a high-quality healing medicine!
  • Synth [X-Heal] @ EL 100. If you don't already have the recipe
  • synth a [Heal Jar] to obtain the recipe in a cutscene.

Combat III: Chain

Lorr

Defeat the target with a high chain attack!

Symbology I: Basics

Isolde

Find the ancient device and activate it!
  • Password = "Dill". For an [A]
  • reach the deepest part of the Abyss (southwest).

Marathon Event

Zeppel

Run straight to the goal deep in the Heights!
  • Destination = Huffin tree
  • though there are two fights on the way there.

Alchemy History

Investigate the Wind's Corridor environment!

Activate the altar in the upper-left area of <Wind's Corridor: Mist> and gaher 20 items.

Synthesis V: Application

"Neatly" synthesize a [Teraflame]!

"Neatly" means that it should have "Detailed" as an Ether Effect (15<=EL<=25).

Synthesis VI: Cooking

Melanie

Synthesize a [Red Soup] so that the teacher likes it!
  • For Melanie to like it
  • the soup should have an Ether Effect of "Flaming Spicy" (EL: 0-15)

Combat IV: Preservation

Lorr

Avoid fighting and head deeper into the ruins!

Destination = where the C6 Tony/Renee fight was. Avoid all combat to earn an [A]. You may use [Treasure Cape].

Synthesis VII: Equipment

Zeppel

Find a Flask at the depths of the Resource Center!

Go to the two targets to obtain [Rusty Flask] and the recipe for [Flask of Galileo]. Turn in the synthesized flask.

Synthesis VIII: Attack

Isolde

Defeat the target using only items!

Just bring a handful of [Globe] and throw those.

Naturology II

Complete the map of <Wind's Corridor: Abyss>!
  • You only need to enter each region of the map
  • though your map is confiscated before the assignment starts.

Combat V: Power

Lorr

Burst to defeat the target by dealing large damage!

「Dunkelknight」 is weak to Fire. Quickly perform a Burst + Finishing Burst.

Symbology II

Isolde

Find the three emblems and analyze them!
  • Explore the ruins to find the three emblems. The in-class answers are (1) "Keeps the campus afloat"
  • (2) "Amplifies Mana powers across the entire campus"
  • (3) "a Mana".

Synthesis IX: Application

Synthesize the ultimate remedy!

Synth [Elixir] @ EL 100.

Combat VI: Speed

Lorr

Defeat the target!
  • Defeat the target before it escapes. Bring Nikki and Anna for their speed
  • put Vayne in Support
  • and throw [Teraflame] to Burst
  • then use Variable Strike + Finishing Bursts until the fight is over.

Combat VII: Chain

Lorr

Defeat the target with your max chain attack!
  • We're looking for number of HITs for one attack chain
  • not maximum damage. For an [A]
  • you'll need at least 20 HIT. One strategy (34 HIT) is: Anna's Dancing Blade Chaos
  • followed by a Variable Strike using Philo
  • Muppy
  • and Vayne in Support.

IMMUNE

In order to avoid fighting 「Crazed Eye」, we must avoid inishing a finale character quest and get Vayne's ending. Many non-finale character quests (i.e., Philo I/II/III/IV, Nikki I/II, Pamela I, Roxis I/II/III/IV, Anna I, and Muppy I/II/III) can still be completed. This means that the following character quest trophies can still be obtained on this run:

With this space, I wish to...
Enact your final wish.

Was it... a joke?
Learn about Philo's mysterious illness.
Complete Philo III.

Hey!
Learn how Nikki attracts all the guys.
Listen to Nikki's song in the Workshop Hallway after completing Nikki II.

This is... a Mana's...
Help Roxis form a contract with the Mana of Light.
Complete Roxis II.

...without this alchemy...
See Muppy's expulsion overturned and the hostage situation resolved.
Complete Muppy III.
